snippet: Empellón Cocina, Alex Stupak’s second Mexican restaurant, opens in the East Village, and Ted & Honey Cafe opens at the Brooklyn Navy Yard.
abstract: Restaurants Empellon Cocina, Don Antonio by Starita, Battery Place Market at 200 West, Food Truck Court, Hummus & Pita Co, Numero 28 Pizzeria Napoletana, Pane Panelle, Ted & Honey Cafe at Bldg 92, Thymari, The Toucan and the Lion, and Yefsi Estiatorio open in New York.
lead_paragraph: Empellón Cocina, Alex Stupak’s second Mexican restaurant, opens in the East Village, and Ted & Honey Cafe opens at the Brooklyn Navy Yard.

headline.seo: Empellón Cocina Opens, Ted & Honey Expands
